item.title: How do you insert a bank stall where ever you want?
item.dc:creator: @Jpspkz Jpspkz
item.description:
@Jpspkz wrote:

[quote=“lets use dds, post:3, topic:196322”]If you have already added fedexer’s global object tut search for

public void NewObjects()

and under it heres an example of what to add:

makeGlobalObject(2896, 10201, 2213, -1, 10);

I think 2213 is bank, the first 2 numbers are coords

Um, like this: makeGlobalobject(1111, 1111, 0, 10); // bank booth

1111, 1111
x coords - first 1111, y coords second 1111, 0 is height lvl i believe, idk what the 10 is, but every other bank booth has 10 so just leave it at that

0 isnt the height, its the direction the object faces, (use 0,-1,-2,-3) and 10 is the object type(most are 10)[/quote]

Thanks
